# Changelog

All notable changes to the orchestrating-integration-development skill.

## [2026-01-14] - P0 Requirement Description Alignment

### Changed
- Updated CheckAffiliation requirement descriptions to reference Pattern A/B/C instead of 'external API query' (aligns with developing-integrations 2026-01-14 update)
- Updated Pagination requirement descriptions to allow 'maxPages OR API signal' instead of mandating 'maxPages constant' (aligns with developing-integrations 2026-01-14 update)

### Fixed
- Inconsistency between orchestrating-integration-development SKILL.md and developing-integrations library skill P0 patterns
- Phase 3 Design section (lines 285-286) now correctly references flexible patterns
- Phase 4.5 P0 Requirements table (lines 360, 363) now matches authoritative source
- Phase 4.5 Gate Checklist (lines 377, 380) now matches authoritative source
- Exit Criteria section (lines 853, 856) now matches authoritative source

### Files Modified
- SKILL.md (8 inline edits across 6 locations)

### Context
The developing-integrations library skill was updated 2026-01-14 to support:
- CheckAffiliation Pattern A (direct API query), Pattern B (CheckAffiliationSimple), Pattern C (seed-based)
- Pagination: maxPages constant OR API-provided signals (LastPage, HasMore, NextToken)

This update ensures orchestrating-integration-development references match the flexible patterns now accepted by the authoritative source.

